<title>
DTC Table
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
The headlight washer system is controlled by the headlight auto leveling and washer control module.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Headlight auto leveling and washer control module have self-diagnosis function that stores content (DTC) of a detected error. A recorded DTC will be retained until it is cleared.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
DTC can be read by selecting “Headlight Auto Leveling” menu on SUZUKI scan tool.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.906in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.052in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "2.667in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.575in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
DTC
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
DTC name
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
